reviewText: Excellent b-movie horror, wll worth a watch!
Fast service great price. Will buy from this merchant again. Thanks

this movie has been the absolute closest thing i've ever seen on tv (TCM) to what my dreams are about since i was about 13 yrs. old....very unsettling to me....but i went ahead and bought the dvd anyways & i'm glad i did...i have watched it several times and the quality is perfect !!!....the shipping was super fast and the seller was BETTER THAN GREAT to deal with...i would definately buy from them again !!!!!
